SUMMARY:Geeks Who Drink Trivia
DTSTAMP:20260325T060140Z
DTSTART:20260408T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:Q: Who helped pioneer the craft beer movement in Seattle by cre
	ating a friendly inclusive environment along side one of the best beer sel
	ections in the city? A: Chuck's Hop Shop Greenwood! Join us for Trivia Nig
	ht every Tuesday. Flex your brain while enjoying beers and BBQ from Woodsh
	op BBQ! Free to play with prizes for the top three teams!\n\nhttps://seato
	day.6amcity.com/events/#/details/geeks-who-drink-trivia/16796869/2026-04-0
	7T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Food & Drink
